gmail - simple webkit-based browser
===================================
gmail is a simple kiosk for mail.google.com Web browser based on
WebKit/GTK+.

Requirements
------------
In order to build gmail you need GTK+ and Webkit/GTK+ header files.

Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (gmail is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install gmail (if
necessary as root):

    make clean install

Running gmail
-------------
run
	gmail
